    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition example that presents nicely and has clearly been cared for. It\u2019s clean and tidy overall, with the kind of normal age-related wear you\u2019d expect, but it still shows very well and feels like a solid, enjoyable car to own. A strong value for someone looking for an honest, attractive driver.",
