    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition vehicle that presents nicely overall and should make a solid, dependable driver. It shows normal signs of use for its age, with some light cosmetic wear inside and out, but nothing out of line for a properly used and cared-for vehicle. The interior is clean and usable, the exterior still shows well, and it runs and drives as it should. A good choice for someone who wants a clean, honest vehicle without expecting showroom perfection.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that presents well and should be enjoyable to own and drive. The exterior shows nicely overall with the normal cosmetic wear you would expect from an older vehicle, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. Inside, the cabin is tidy and complete with typical signs of age and use, yet still a comfortable and respectable place to spend time. This is not a fully restored or near-new showpiece, but it is a solid, well-kept car that offers a strong balance of presentation, usability, and value for a buyer looking for a good driver-quality example.",
      "price": 32800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle is a smart choice for buyers seeking straightforward value. It shows age and wear consistent with an inexpensive used car, yet still offers solid utility for commuting, errands, or as a backup vehicle. A budget-friendly opportunity to get on the road without overspending.",
      "price": 6450.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a practical runaround. It has the honest wear you\u2019d expect at this stage, but it still offers great value and a chance to get on the road without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and worth a look if you appreciate a straightforward deal.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast upside. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis still feels composed, and it presents as a usable platform for someone who appreciates mechanical honesty over cosmetics. Not a showroom car, but a straightforward, analog machine with plenty of serviceable life for a hands-on owner, track toy build, or budget performance commuter. Priced to reflect condition while leaving room for the next owner to sort the details and enjoy it.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Honest poor-condition driver with wear, flaws, and plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real presence and a story still being written. It has the kind of honest, lived-in character that makes it perfect for someone who sees potential where others see a weekend project. Whether you want an affordable set of wheels, a hands-on restoration candidate, or a dependable companion for tinkering and back-road adventures, this one offers a chance to make it your own without a big upfront spend. A little vision will go a long way here.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable, honest-value vehicle with solid potential for the right buyer. This car is being offered as a budget-friendly option for local driving, a starter vehicle, or a hands-on project. It shows its age and will benefit from attention, but it presents a practical opportunity to own a vehicle at an accessible price point. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive transportation with room to make it your own, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
